title: MixZle v1.5
description:
MixZle is a fascinating game that will stimulate your creativity and challenge your logical skills in a captivating way. Easy to learn and intuitive to play, MixZle uses an accurate physics system to provide ingenious levels where the goal is putting the ball into the net.

Each level presents you with a different array of objects and tools that you must arrange to carry the ball into the hoop.
If you like puzzles and challenging games, then MixZle is for you. Containing over a hundred levels, this game will literally exercite your neurons.

REMARK:
Requires Android 2.2 or later and devices running the ArmV7 processor.

What's New:

This update fixes some permission issues that were preventing the game from launching on some devices.
